<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Please login and complete the recruiting steps to proceed</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 24px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #374151;
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      a {
        color: #0b74de;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      p {
        margin: 0 0 12px 0;
      }
      strong {
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      ul {
        margin: 8px 0 16px 24px;
        padding: 0;
      }
      li {
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <p>Hi {!Receiving_User.Display_Name__c},</p>

    <p>To better understand your experience and background, we ask clinicians to complete a few short tasks in our portal. This only takes a few minutes.</p>

    <p>
      To get started, visit
      <a href="{!Community_Url}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        {!Community_Name}
      </a>
      and login using your personal email address.
    </p>

    
    <p>Thank you,
    <br />{!Organization.Name}</p>
  </body>
</html>